WEBVTT

00:00:08.974 --> 00:00:13.194
 The Republic of Alernia has issued a civil warning to all citizens.

00:00:14.074 --> 00:00:17.454
 A classified specimen has escaped from the National Laboratory.

00:00:18.154 --> 00:00:20.434
 An emergency has been declared in the nation.

00:00:22.137 --> 00:00:30.537
 If you see an exigent homunculus-esque creature outside of your home, lock all doors, turn off all lights and anything powered by electricity.

00:00:31.157 --> 00:00:34.357
 Go into a basement, closet, or barricaded room.

00:00:34.817 --> 00:00:37.697
 Do not leave until the creature has seized all noise.

00:00:38.157 --> 00:00:41.117
 After the end of all noises, call authorities immediately.

00:00:41.737 --> 00:00:46.637
 Anyone interacting with this creature shall be considered a fugitive, if they live long enough.